dBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:39:23.000Z","msg":"中共「七個做得到」：<br />\n孝 悌 忠 信 禮 義 廉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:52:31.000Z","msg":"一招「無恥即無敵」獨步天下"},{"pid":"eed75c09e76f773d5437acc253ae6bcc48e54597","tid":1890602,"uid":103374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:55:34.000Z","msg":"美國只有2個做唔到<br />\n1. 做唔到疫情係國內大規模爆發<br />\n2. 就算有疫情都做唔到支那人咁厚面皮無視國民苦況仲要話其他國的不是"},{"pid":"2ff18d1854e47c5175f4742268c9898d4ebbcda0","tid":1890602,"uid":103916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:57:33.000Z","msg":"捉番佢，返動物園啦。"},{"pid":"d572298ef3f1db0f4eda4b944da7ad2f39629cfb","tid":1890602,"uid":265044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T10:03:29.000Z","msg":"總括八個做不到，就係中共能撐大眼講大話，美國能做得到嗎？"},{"pid":"9f0ec389f358ec0c76c5f7942a7a469c19d1cb86","tid":1890602,"uid":284032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T11:06:06.000Z","msg":"至少美國做到唔興食蝙蝠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}